{{menutrail|Main menu}}
{{menutrail|Main menu|Game files menu}}
[[File:LoadGameMenu.png|thumb|The load game menu in {{dw|Epic 2}}.]]The '''load game menu''' allows access to the list of [[savegame|saved games]] made from the played [[IWAD]]. Saves created with the same selection of mods are displayed in white; saves created with mods not currently loaded are displayed in orange and cannot be loaded. Its [[MENUDEF]] name is {{c|LoadGameMenu}} and it can be summoned with the {{c|{{CCMD|O|menu_load}}}} console command.

Hitting the "delete" key allows to manually delete a saved game. [[ZDoom]] will ask you for confirmation before erasing the file.
